doclets.name: toMaybe
doclets.description: Change the Identity to a Some Maybe.

Identity is a monad that has only one state. It has all the monad operations but will always return the same state type. It is useful as a way to compose functions.

import {Identity} from 'fronads';

const add = aa => bb => aa + bb;

Identity(5)
    .map(add(2))
    .map(add(-10))
    .value();
// -3


// Hocking a React component.
Some(UserProfile)
    .map(connect(({user}) => ({user}))
    .value();
doclets.comment:
/**
 * Identity is a monad that has only one state. It has all the monad operations but
 * will always return the same state type.
 * It is useful as a way to compose functions.
 *
 * ```js
 * import {Identity} from 'fronads';
 *
 * const add = aa => bb => aa + bb;
 *
 * Identity(5)
 *     .map(add(2))
 *     .map(add(-10))
 *     .value();
 * // -3
 *
 *
 * // Hocking a React component.
 * Some(UserProfile)
 *     .map(connect(({user}) => ({user}))
 *     .value();
 * ```
 * @module Identity
 */
